prompts.frontCover: A charming and funny cartoon-style watercolor illustration of a capybara wearing a tiny, festive party hat, looking blissfully happy while soaking in a yuzu hot spring. The capybara is surrounded by several floating yuzu fruits, one of which also has a miniature party hat on it. The scene is rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds. In the center of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday to my favorite capybara, Lao Lao". The overall design is flat 2D, perfect for printing.
